originalText.text: I highly recommend this practice, I was a patient of the midwives while pregnant and have also seen Drs. Moritz and Lee - both of whom are phenomenal.  Like any office, there can be some issues with wait time but the care you get once you're in front of the providers is unparalleled.

originalText.text: If I could give this place ZERO stars, I would. This is the worst doctors office I’ve ever been to. I had to wait over an hour for my 7pm appointment. Didn’t see my doctor until 8:10pm and before that was moved to THREE different rooms. After I was finally seen, my convo with the doctor was 10 MINUTES. You can tell that the doctor was rushed and did not care. He then told me to make an appointment with the receptionist for my next exam. I then go up to an empty receptionist and look for someone to assist me. I finally manage to flag someone down and she tells me that the receptionist is gone and that I have to call back the next day to schedule my OWN appt. This office is the biggest joke and have never been to a more unprofessional place. I’ve wasted 2.5 hours of my time and I would never recommend this place to anyone!!
